```
It says, that you calculate the position which is a bit to the right of the player&#39;s right side, and then check the left-top and the right-bottom tiles, i.e. tiles shown by green color on the previous picture. Do you see the problem now? You should check the **right**-top and the right-bottom tiles. However, because of your mistake the collision of the right-top corner with the wall is not detected and the player is allowed to move further, inside the wall.

