  [2]: https://stackoverflow.com/revisions/34322364/3
  [3]: https://stackoverflow.com/a/10479208/2668136
  [4]: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/7230893/android-search-with-fragments
  [5]: http://www.javaworld.com/article/2077258/learn-java/observer-and-observable.html
  [6]: http://www.tutorialspoint.com/java/util/observable_addobserver.htm

