Edit: &lt;s&gt;The downside is that you MUST have &#39;log.level&#39; always set.  The way I deal with this is to check in my main method and set it to INFO if not already set, be sure to do this before you first logging calls.  Then I can override on the command line, and have a sensible default. &lt;/s&gt;

Here is how it looks in my logback.xml:

